Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉羅  沒有什麼關於硫加的新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有最新資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是從麥基烏斯警官那裡傳送過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警官那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像存在把硫加從宿主身上分離的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗官解讀的古文書中  硫加的第三階段變異
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班蒂羅態時會收縮到宿主體內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候可以轉移到別的生物上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轉移後  硫加將和新的宿主一起成長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在顯現之前停止宿主的生命活動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能捕獲硫加了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離班蒂羅狀態還有多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估計在一小時以內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在這段時間內阻止硫加的行動  避免傷害到地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萊拉羅  潛行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加擬態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用牽引光線把它拉到海裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就這麼拉到海裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能量裝填  15%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要變成班蒂羅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（班蒂羅是巴西的一種有點像椅子的打擊樂器，據說演奏起來很華麗，\N這裡應該單純指琉加的形狀變化和這種樂器相似吧……）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用星體作業破壞硫加的身體後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進行淨化之儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地表47%將被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是從這裡無法進行淨化之儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚮導的任務就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,困住硫加擬態  只能維持15個單位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出去  開倉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香  逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟夏瑪朗在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死了  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個身體的意識在抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很難據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個男人幫我把這力量除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:06:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喚醒我的人都因我而毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知性生命體為什麼希望同族的死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有高度發達的智能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的生命們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這些愚蠢的生命之間遊走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並將其消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓真正的寂靜降臨這個宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把小夜香還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是小夜香  也是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你沒阻止  小夜香才會去夏瑪朗身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我覺醒的時候攻擊了那個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山  樹  房子  人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我身邊最喜歡的人總是會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽  爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉爺爺的是夏瑪朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,良枝阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,良枝阿姨是被我吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再過一會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能完全吞噬掉這個世界所有的知性生命體了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為世界就要在這裡終結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  功君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓再你離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始我一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要明白  中杉同學已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但中杉同學還沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有完全變成硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了她的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許能夠救她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宿主又開始反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消滅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  比預想的成長還要快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退下  功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是硫加的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還在繼續成長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全成長後就會開始殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加  硫加不會殺宿主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估計  或許還能來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學或許還有救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以功你也別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧  這宿主已經屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  小夜香還沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和功君一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  和我一起見證人類的滅亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  想和我一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加  我和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  快從小夜香那裡出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  硫加  到我的身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼這麼傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪也想過同樣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓硫加寄生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連同自己一起處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是聯邦搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望巴迪死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁硫加還沒有奪去我的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加的封印完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個能給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍人什麼時候能給神祗官下命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是拜託你  對你也不是件壞事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗廳中也有協助我們的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗廳中？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聰明點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能封印這個多虧了某個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們法庭見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,六本木大破壞的犧牲者數量目前依然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前東京上空有大型低氣壓停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人證言目擊到大規模落雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  啪嚓一下  真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車…我的車被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  這個是等離子  等·離·子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏瑪朗下落不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從Lost Bird號沉沒到現在還沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傳媒界的風雲人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管出現的時候還是消失的時候都會成為話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,局裡一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是上層追隨夏瑪朗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂天上不會掉餡餅吧\N驕る平家は久しからず
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因為六本木毀滅事件  現場大恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在好像對夏瑪朗的事沒興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡  你們這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩  你是不是知道點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不敢肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不敢肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定地球正在面臨著空前的大慘案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是平時那種荒唐的消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lost  Bird沉沒  夏瑪朗下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭啊  中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我平時不怎麼來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能和大家成為朋友  現在卻要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記我們  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我會給你們寫信的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  你們倆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是不能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊學校的情況  發簡訊告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轉學第一天最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕  第一天就強勢點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文靜的中杉怎麼能做出那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且身體還沒完全恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保重  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  雖然我們平時沒怎麼說話  你也保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫千川同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不過挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指失去這三個月的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連她爺爺去世後的那些事情都忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想著你能和中杉順利發展的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  在那裡消沉什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人最後總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且重要的人或許就在身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪  這次我的身體什麼時候能恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毀得一塌糊塗了  這次可能很費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說了讓你殺掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微手下留情點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  突然之間…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被人看見了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  功是我的搭檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和這沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個就是把硫加封印了的聯邦搜查官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希馮·阿魯提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還有點嫩  但直覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的孩子  巴迪·希馮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,==================================
